DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260716
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260717
SUMMARY:S: Contact Kerry on her return — lock in concrete coffee/studio vis
 it
DESCRIPTION:Kerry is east for eldercare\, back mid-July. Her cue was "would
  be\nlovely to catch up after that" — and the 6/25 reply deliberately left
 \nit open.  Don't wait for her to ping: propose a *specific* day (coffee\n
 or studio visit in the pentagonal ring)\, per the plan's beat (3). Also\nr
 e-raise the Aphasia "Together" clip if the password is still\nunresolved.\
 n\nMichael drafts. Three beats: (1) thanks — /Standardized Patient/ link\n
 worked\, clip downloaded. (2) the /Aphasia Poetry Club/ password\n`Aphasia
 2015' is *rejected* by the site (verified — not a typo on our\nend)\; ask 
 her to re-check it or just send the "Together" clip\ndirectly.  (3) propos
 e a *concrete* coffee/studio visit after she's\nback mid-July — don't leav
 e it open-ended.
CATEGORIES:cal,org-calendar-staging
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T233700Z
UID:TS1-122CD07F-F58F-4F93-ADD5-13CC3F6B26C8
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260626
SUMMARY:reply draft (to send) [2026-06-25 Thu]
DESCRIPTION:Hi Kerry!  Thanks for these: was able to grab Standardized Pati
 ent -\nAphasia password didn’t work for me though!\n\n… and thanks for the
  kind words re: Return — means a great deal…\n\nsorry to hear that you hav
 e eldercare to do - my mom had a very long\nand difficult passage - became
  quite consuming for a number of years -\nhoping you will have an easier t
 ime of it.\n\nI’ll hit you back up after your return - or feel free to pin
 g me as\nwell! Looking forward to catching up for real for real.\n\nXX m\n
 \n/Consonance note:/ matches beats (1) thanks/Standardized-Patient and\n(2
 ) flag bad Aphasia pw — but (2) doesn't explicitly ask her to\nre-check th
 e pw or send "Together" directly\, and (3) the catch-up\nclose is left *op
 en-ended* ("I'll hit you back up after your return")\,\nthe exact deferral
  the plan + self-pattern #4 warn against. Defensible\ngiven she's mid-elde
 rcare-travel (a hard mid-July date is hard to pin\nnow)\, but a light tigh
 tening would honor the plan\, e.g. "once you're\nback mid-July let's actua
 lly lock something in — coffee or come by the\nstudio." Adds (good\, not i
 n the planned beats): thanks for the RTT\nkind words.\n\n• Serious institu
 tional artist\, well-connected in LA and beyond.\n• Worked together on mul
 tiple major pieces including Hammer premiere.\n• *Married to Mungo Thomson
 * — same household\; outreach to both in the\n  same window will be notice
 d. Space by 2–3 weeks at minimum.\n• Has vouched for you to Aram in the pa
 st (the 2019 DMX/Qlab\n  referral).  She's already an active advocate\, no
 t a cold ask.\n• *Approach:* zero-ask email.\n• *Possible later asks:* loo
 k at excerpt\, suggest contacts.
CATEGORIES:org-calendar-staging
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
